OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged historic
OL,4,Csexual abuse at Scottish Borders school
OL,6,FPolice are investigating reports of
OL,7,Fhistoric sexual abuse at a secondary
OL,8,Fschool in the Borders.
OL,10,FThe alleged incidents took place in
OL,11,FGalashiels between 1969 and 1980.
OL,13,FThe school has not been named by
OL,14,FPolice Scotland, but is understood to
OL,15,Fbe Galashiels Academy.
