OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged historic
OL,4,Csexual abuse at Scottish Borders school
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Jim McLauchlan of
OL,7,FPolice Scotland's National Child Abuse
OL,8,FInvestigation Unit said: "We take all
OL,9,Freports of sexual abuse extremely
OL,10,Fseriously and ask anyone who believes
OL,11,Fthey may have been a victim to come
OL,12,Fforward, regardless of the passage of
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,F"We know that those with information
OL,16,Ffrom this time period may no longer
OL,17,Flive in the area and we want to
OL,18,Fencourage everyone with knowledge of
OL,19,Fthis type of crime to reach out.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUwD@AOU
